short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Keep track of the links sent in Google Meet chats in one handy place

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: People sometimes send useful links in a Google Meet chat but there's no way of retrieving those unless you've recorded the session with transcript. This Chrome extension automatically saves all links sent in a Google Meet chat and displays them in the handy popup (when you click the icon in the extension bar).
